8F189F049B19C36A909D49D5406","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Centrifuge 20ml of a healthy micro-algal culture in log phase of growth. Resuspend the pellet in fresh media sterilize through a 0.1 or 0.22 \u00b5m filter. If it is possible, check the media a priori by flow cytometer (FC) for bacteria contaminant. <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-style:italic;\">The speed and time of the centrifugation will vary among the different groups of algae. For E.hux, Christian Jeanthon used 1600g during 2\u2019. <\/span><span><\/span><\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":919185,"guid":"AE7A99A180F311EAA4A93DBDB597EA1B","previous_id":919194,"previous_guid":"FD6822D080F311EAA4A93DBDB597EA1B","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"CE9AE438E7D84103A13CC879DC3B3A14","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"80BFCA27E2964DADA62A90CA614CA0AE","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Resuspend the cells in 600 \u00b5l of fresh sterile media.\n<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-style:italic;\">The inoculum should be dense therefore the volume to resuspend the cells and to add in the next step can be changed accordingly. <\/span><\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":919186,"guid":"AE7C6E6080F311EAA4A93DBDB597EA1B","previous_id":919185,"previous_guid":"AE7A99A180F311EAA4A93DBDB597EA1B","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"0FD6A9CB298B4D45B2BB1C9C7E760FE4","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"gu